# The Compose build context is the shared Projects directory so the workspace
# can resolve the sibling prosopikon crate. Keep generated artifacts and local
# checkouts out of the context while retaining both source trees.
**
!DASObjectStore/
!DASObjectStore/**
!prosopikon/
!prosopikon/**

DASObjectStore/target
DASObjectStore/node_modules
DASObjectStore/playwright-report
DASObjectStore/test-results
prosopikon/target
prosopikon/node_modules
